race.comment: CHILLY CHARLIE (2) turned in a much better run last time when letting it all unfold before charging home into second. This is no tougher and looKs hard to hold out again. PHAROAH'S DAUGHTER (12) has been racing well run-in on into the placings lately. Looks ideally placed this line-up and will be tough to stop again. LA ROSETTA (5) returns after a long spell and presents on the back of a Tatura trial win. Has good early speed so should take up a forward position. Should be involved in the finish. FIFI BLUE (1) placed fresh and is fitter again. Doesn't win out of turn but has placed 2/3 when second-up. Claim helps and will be winding up late.
